{"tid":2117860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有網友話連登仔成日提721好煩","createTime":"2020-07-21T06:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T07:25:44.000Z","uid":186294,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"07a9a6d7399837f7d91752464d00c05090a298d0","tid":2117860,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"但如果我地唔重覆講完又講，就會俾港共政權得逞，扭曲歷史，如下圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tU0uHy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtU0uHy5.jpg&h=35c4ab92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：端傳媒<br />\n<br />\n由於端傳媒既專題文章係會員付費形式，為尊重記者付出，我只摘錄兩小段：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">端傳媒同時翻查中國大陸的官媒報道，發現大多數報導或文章都沿用這樣一條故事線：黑衣人挑釁引發暴力衝突&mdash;&mdash;白衣人「教訓」暴力示威者&mdash;&mdash;民主派散播謊言誤導輿論；而在這論述中，白衣人是「保衛家園」一派。<br />\n《環球時報》引述親建制團體「幫港出聲」的言論指，「元朗事件之前，已有多個小區的居民自發組織起來抵抗『遍地開花』，並發生衝突事件。因此，元朗事件並不是偶然事件。」而身為紅三代的內地網絡意見領袖、在反修例運動期間多次發文的兔主席，則將白衣人施襲描述為「社會組織企圖自救」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">見倒呢一年入面港共政權不斷篡改歷史，搶奪話語權，蒙蔽我地下一代，仲有機會扭曲國際上對721事件既理解<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盡最大既努力將鏗鏘集條片、眾新聞721專題網頁、任何關於721真相既資料喺fb ig share出去，周街唔小心漏低721真相文章，甚至口耳相傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34bd0dc68ae2dd5aa7f787488481fd45fe024aa","tid":2117860,"uid":60000,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d37c2ccb589bcb27f90e20dde42a392ffbe0e1","tid":2117860,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=or4B7NpHwbY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dor4B7NpHwbY&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=55dd9769\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=or4B7NpHwbY</a><br />\n<br />\n怒share系列：<br />\n1. 鏗鏘集"},{"pid":"b74ae43712cae994ec59646d8d7f0ebb2513a672","tid":2117860,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"六四無死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部都係外國勢力老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要過30年 其實好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d0b10cf35d5e334f11723db645868cf170a725","tid":2117860,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/infographic-721/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Finfographic-721%2F&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=623896f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/infographic-721/</a><br />\n<br />\n怒share系列：<br />\n呢個網係眾新聞整既721專題網站，圖文並茂，用電腦睇更佳"},{"pid":"5f2fbf1aae015b2b935229373c08ed72c178741d","tid":2117860,"uid":267494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"所以話<br />\n南京事件都不過係一件襲擊事件<br />\n有中國人攻擊日軍<br />\n日本又有人帶隊入去還擊<br />\n所以事情搞大左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec66573aa679838d43fb1f753aef9cf3d9fff38","tid":2117860,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyGar8M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyGar8M.png&h=9c7309a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有柳俊江撈埋黑警嗰份，幫黑警查埋案，還原真相"},{"pid":"b9d6c987e6ca2f9137630d02903368913ddf7166","tid":2117860,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f2fbf1aae015b2b935229373c08ed72c178741d","tid":2117860,"uid":267494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"所以話<br />\n南京事件都不過係一件襲擊事件<br />\n有中國人攻擊日軍<br />\n日本又有人帶隊入去還擊<br />\n所以事情搞大左<br />\n<img src=